displayName: Turipa Village - Temporary Home of the Advanced Magicians

parameters: Advanced Mage: Please don't disturb my research.
Who are you all, advanced sorcerers?
Clea: Are you all advanced sorcerers from the Magic Academy?

Clea: Actually, there is something we would like your
cooperation with. This is a directive from the Archmage.

Advanced Sorcerer: I see... I understand. Our research has
also reached a dead end, so this will be a refreshing change
of pace.

Sorceress Relm: What kind of research are you conducting
here?

Advanced Sorcerer: I can't say it out loud, but I suspect
there is an ancient civilization.

Advanced Sorcerer: The noble Ect is uncooperative... so
let's head to the noble Casaro's place first.

Assistant to the Advanced Sorcerer: I can't believe I got
sent to Valier... sigh.

Assistant to the Advanced Sorcerer: I am a magician, but I
am actually a follower of the Terios religion...

Assistant to the Advanced Sorcerer: I feel relieved after
sharing this with you. The Academy and the Terios religion
don't get along well, you know.

Assistant to the Advanced Sorcerer: Once upon a time, the
Terios Church and the Academy were united, but the world has
become a difficult place for someone like me to live in.
